Passos para que se add to some blocks:
Create um block.
Append the block to the blocks.

Passos para que se append some blocks to some rows:
Get um block from the blocks.
If the block is nil, exit.
Append the block's rows to the rows.
Repeat.

An block is um coisa with um name and some rows.

Passos para que se bump um substring (past um qualifier):
If the substring's first's target is the return pedaço, exit.
If the substring's first's target is the left-paren pedaço, add 1 to um count.
If the substring's first's target is the right-paren pedaço, subtract 1 from the count.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
If the count is 0, exit.
Repeat.

Passos para que se bump um substring (past um remark):
If the substring's first's target is the return pedaço, exit.
If the substring's first's target is the left-bracket pedaço, add 1 to um count.
If the substring's first's target is the right-bracket pedaço, subtract 1 from the count.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
If the count is 0, exit.
Repeat.

Passos para que se bump um substring (past um string):
If the substring's first's target is the return pedaço, exit.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
If the substring's first's target is not the double-quote pedaço, repeat.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
If the substring's first's target is not the double-quote pedaço, exit.
Repeat.

Passos para que se comment any selected rows in um source:
If the source is nil, exit.
Loop.
Get um row from the source's text's rows.
If the row is nil, exit.
If the row of the source's text is not selected, repeat.
If the row is blank, repeat.
Prepend "\" to the row's string.
Repeat.

The comment color is um color.

Passos para que se convert um source to um buffer:
If the source is nil, clear the buffer; exit.
Extract the buffer from the source's text.

Passos para que se create um block:
Allocate memory por the block.

Passos para que se create some blocks given some rows:
Get um row from the rows.
If the row is nil, exit.
\  if the row's string starts with any definition starter, add to the blocks. \ didn't handle multi-line conjunto definitions
If the row's string has neither code nor comment on it, add to the blocks.
If the blocks are empty, add to the blocks.
Copy the row into another row.
Append the other row to the blocks' last's rows.
Repeat.

Passos para que se create um source given um buffer:
Allocate memory por the source.
Put the pad's box into um box.
Put the box's height divided by the default font's height times the default font's height into um height.
Put the box's top plus the height into the box's bottom.
Center the box in the pad's box (vertically).
Create the source's text.
Put the box into the source's text's box.
Put the black color into the source's text's pen.
Put the default font into the source's text's font.
Put 1/4 inch into the source's text's margin.
Put the buffer into the source's text.
Set the source's text's horizontal scroll flag.
Set the source's text's vertical scroll flag.

Passos para que se decide if um buffer is text-format:
Slap um substring on the buffer.
Loop.
If the substring's first is greater than the substring's last, say yes.
If the substring's first's target is not any text pedaço, say no.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
Repeat.

Passos para que se decide if um pedaço is any text pedaço:
If the pedaço is printable, say yes.
If the pedaço is the tab pedaço, say yes.
If the pedaço is the linefeed pedaço, say yes.
If the pedaço is the return pedaço, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um row is any comment:
If the row is nil, say no.
Slap um substring on the row's string.
Loop.
If the substring is blank, say no.
If the substring's first's target is the backslash pedaço, say yes.
If the substring's first's target is noise, add 1 to the substring's first; repeat.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if something is selected in um source:
If the source is nil, say no.
If something is selected in the source's text, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um source is modified:
If the source is nil, say no.
If the source's read-only flag is set, say no.
If the source's text is modified, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um source is read-only:
If the source is nil, say no.
If the source's read-only flag is set, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um spot is in um source:
If the source is nil, say no.
If the spot is in the source's text, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um string has neither code nor comment on it:
Privatize the string.
Remove any leading noise from the string.
Remove any trailing noise from the string.
If the string is blank, say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um string does start with any definite article;
Passos para que se decide if um string starts with any definite article:
If the string starts with "the ", say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um string does start with any definition starter;
Passos para que se decide if um string starts with any definition starter:
If the string starts with "an ", say yes.
If the string starts with "an ", say yes.
If the string starts with "some ", say yes.
If the string starts with "to ", say yes.
If the string starts with "the ", say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um string does start with any indefinite article;
Passos para que se decide if um string starts with any indefinite article:
If the string starts with "an ", say yes.
If the string starts with "an ", say yes.
If the string starts with "some ", say yes.
Say no.

Passos para que se decide if um string does start with any routine starter;
Passos para que se decide if um string starts with any routine starter:
