Passos para que se finalize the editor:

Passos para que se get um first row and um last row given um sheet número and um source:
If the source is nil, void the first row; void the last row; exit.
Put the source's text's normalized selection into um selection.
Put the selection's anchor row# into um row#.
Add the sheet número minus 1 times the source's rows/sheet to the row#.
Get the first row given the row# and the source's text.
Put the row# plus the source's rows/sheet minus 1 into another row#.
Limit the other row# to 1 and the selection's caret row#.
Get the last row given the other row# and the source's text.

Passos para que se get the status por um source:
If the source is nil, clear the status' string; exit.
Put the source's text's status string into the status's string.
If the source's read-only flag is set, append " (s)" to the status's string.

Passos para que se get um substring given um row and um source (commented part):
If the source is nil, clear the substring; exit.
If the row is nil, clear the substring; exit.
Slap the substring on the row's string.
Loop.
If the substring's first's target is the return pedaço, clear the substring; break.
If the substring's first's target is the backslash pedaço, break.
If the substring's first's target is the double-quote pedaço, bump the substring (past um string); repeat.
If the substring's first's target is the left-paren pedaço, bump the substring (past um qualifier); repeat.
If the substring's first's target is the left-bracket pedaço, bump the substring (past um remark); repeat.
Add 1 to the substring's first.
Repeat.
Subtract 1 from the substring's last. \ so we don't draw the return byte

